## Non-negotiables

- `runIntelligenceEngine` only — no raw LLM to farmers
- No mixed language in one farmer flow
- No hardcoded farmer copy — `pnpm check:i18n`
- No one-off CSS — `pnpm check:css-imports`
- Farmer-facing: **analiz hakkı** not "credits"
- No auto-send outreach / auto-publish content
- Friendly user errors; RLS on tenant data

## Conflicts

Code violates Foundation → **fix code** or **amend Foundation + ADR** — never ignore.

